data.description: Welcome Home to this beautifully maintained 2 story home safely cradled in the cul-de-sac of Misty Lake Subdivision. Enter through the spacious 2 story foyer flanked by a dining room and a office/sitting room. The open floor plan of the living room and kitchen over-look the private backyard oasis. The roomy kitchen has endless solid countertop space and stainless steel appliances. The split bedroom plan upstairs is ideal for privacy. An oversized master bedroom on one end with a luxurious master bathroom, separate tub and shower, is the perfect relaxing getaway. Three secondary bedrooms on the 2nd level share a hall bathroom. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs.   If listing brokerage shows the property, buyer's brokerage commission shall be $500. **Seller is offering a $1800 incentive to buyer if buyer uses our preferred lender, Daniel Taylor with Certainty Home Lending. Active military & law enforcement,  or retired in good standing, get an additional $1000 incentive.**
